{"tid":1902083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獨立媒體：建制北角派口罩 15分鐘散水 市民斥影完相就話無 即獲派發","createTime":"2020-02-28T07:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"769687de1fe9466ae1f32aa9ac7d1f4f9bf76a85","tid":1902083,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）「全港抗疫連線」今日聯同香港福建社團聯會到北角城市花園派發口罩。民建聯副主席陳勇感謝鄉親領袖的努力，指他們用自己的錢買機票，「用行李、用人肉」也務求將口罩送到有需要的人的手上。行動15在分鐘內即結束，眾建制人士隨即「閃人」，有誤以為排不到口罩的市民怒斥「影完相就走」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GW9bfnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGW9bfnb.jpg&h=5e9d726b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n⋯⋯500份口罩不消15分鐘已派光，有排隊尾的市民被告知沒有口罩，一度鼓譟稱「喂你影完相就話冇呀？啲記者走哂先話冇。」該名市民之後才獲分口罩。李慧琼欲離開時接受傳媒訪問，但當《獨媒》記者上前時，李即稱「唔使喇，我好忙呀」並轉身離開，拒絕受訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071126&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=71191344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071126&h=dc93fd8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071126</a><br />\n<br />\n成村人打卡原來派咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n15分鐘連埋影大合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cbd8fb6cf90d592224ab6c789ff9484e318b5f","tid":1902083,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"下次要切埋燒豬"},{"pid":"5c7439108234574605ae906bb6f4b67b14fdddd9","tid":1902083,"uid":243380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地當你傻仔咁撚咋"},{"pid":"1dde1b721801a63528894c68240b2bcd3eecee62","tid":1902083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"佢地真係旨在影張相咋"},{"pid":"c610e699bf5da03c9dfd6cf16e39668c15f54500","tid":1902083,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dde1b721801a63528894c68240b2bcd3eecee62","tid":1902083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"佢地真係旨在影張相咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"貨係深圳攞，影張相玩下廢老"},{"pid":"f4d33088655c48324b0fac2be8e35f54e3921588","tid":1902083,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"空盒嚟架傻西"}]}